</P>
<P>
 Kids can kvetch with critters, learn to play keyboards and more on Sunday, 
Sept. 11, from 11 a.m. to 4 p.m. at the Oak Canyon Nature Center, 6700 Walnut 
Canyon Road. Exhibitors include Bowers Museum, Discovery Science Center and 
Griffith Observatory. Free. (714) 998-8380. 
</P>
