<HEADLINE>
<P>
COLLEGE FOOTBALL PREVIEW / FOOTHILL CONFERENCE; ANTELOPE VALLEY MARAUDERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 1993 OVERALL: 6-5 CONFERENCE: 5-2 PLACE: 3rd 
</P>
