 COACH, YR.: RECORD AT SCHOOL Jim Bittner, 17th: 93-58-2 04,26,05,05,05 PLAYERS 
TO WATCH OFF DEF YR David Acosta, 6-2, 280 -- T So. Oscar Acosta, 6-3, 275 G -- 
