</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 PacBell Says New Area Code Nearly Due: Telephone area code 562 will be 
activated sooner than expected, perhaps within a year, because 310 numbers are 
going fast, said Gene Sherman, Pacific Bell vice president."The demand for 
numbers in 310 has been spectacular, particularly for cellular and paging 
services," he said. "It's undeniable proof that people want to call and be 
called in every setting." Bellcore, the telecommunications organization 
monitoring the North American Numbering Plan, has warned that 310 is "in 
jeopardy," which means demand may exceed the code's capacity before a new one 
can be added. 
</P>
