<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DEBORA VRANA, TIMES STAFF WRITER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Capp Care Inc.: The managed health care provider said Wednesday that it has 
signed a contract with a New York City preferred provider organization that 
will expand Capp Care's coverage into New York and New Jersey. The contract 
with Premier Preferred Care is expected to add 90,000 customers to Capp Care's 
rolls. 
</P>
