Sr. 04,29,05,05,05 TOP NEWCOMERS OFF DEF YR Rashadd Cousins, 6-3, 190 WR -- Jr. 
Bernard Lirgarta, 5-10, 165 WR -- Sr. Jackie Samuel, 5-10, 160 -- DB Jr. FAST 
FACT 
</P>
