<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOOTBALL '94 / HIGH SCHOOL COACHES SHOW OFF THEIR TRICKS!; SOUTHERN SECTION; 
ALPHA LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 KILPATRICK MUSTANGS 03,14,08,07 1993 OVERALL LEAGUE PLACE 3-6 03,12,05,18 
