 OUTLOOK 
</P>
<P>
 Along with the iron-pumping linemen, each of the Coyotes' receivers and 
backfield players run the 40-yard dash under five seconds. Indeed, the 1994 
roster is a collection of strong and fast athletes. But it is a small 
collection, a roster of 30 that Edwards chooses to call the "Dirty 30." Only 10 
seniors and only five starters return. Smith, stronger and three inches taller, 
moves from receiver to QB. MOORPARK MUSKETEERS 03,14,08,07 1993 OVERALL LEAGUE 
