strangely, only 30 players have turned out for the 1994 title defense. Fifteen 
top JV players from last year are sitting out, despite personal pleas from 
Dearborn. NORDHOFF RANGERS 03,14,08,07 1993 OVERALL LEAGUE PLACE 8-4 X3-1 2nd 
