So. Joe Velasquez, 5-9, 165 OL DL Jr. David Alvarez, 5-10, 240 OL DL Jr. FAST 
FACT 
</P>
<P>
 The Falcons played 50 summer passing league games to give a group of 
receivers, including three sophomores, needed experience. 
</P>
<P>
 OUTLOOK 
</P>
<P>
 The Falcons are young and deep. With 51 players on the roster, Palmdale has 20 
more players than a year ago. Paez returns after a one-year absence to take 
over a wide-open attack which produced 2,730 passing yards last year. "We're 
still going to throw a lot and throw all over the field," Williams said. QUARTZ 
