<P>
 FAST FACT 
</P>
<P>
 The Rebels return six starters from an offense which averaged 37.3 points a 
game. 
</P>
<P>
 OUTLOOK Either Kendrid or Woodworth will have the unenviable task of replacing 
Golden League offensive player of the year Brad Norris, who passed for 2,691 
yards and 24 touchdowns. Kendrid, an option specialist, and Woodworth, a 
drop-back passer, will both play in preseason games before Albee settles on a 
starter for the league season. Pereira was Golden League defensive player of 
the year and Adranga was an all-league selection. 
</P>
